---

<section id="services" class="services">
  <div class="services-container">
    <div class="header-content animate-fade-up">
      <p class="subtitle">Our Expertise</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Digital Solutions Built<br/>For Growth</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <!-- Service 1 -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fade-up delay-100">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Google Maps SEO</h3>
        <p>We optimize your Google Business Profile so you show up first when locals search for your exact services.</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Service 2 -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fade-up delay-200">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="3" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Lead-Gen Websites</h3>
        <p>Fast websites packed with AI-enhanced premium visuals that turn casual visitors into high-paying booked jobs.</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Service 3 -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fade-up delay-300">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m21 16-5.16-5.16a2 2 0 0 0-2.83 0l-5.16 5.16"/><path d="m16 11-2.16-2.16a2 2 0 0 0-2.83 0l-4.16 4.16"/><circle cx="8" cy="9" r="2"/><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Bespoke Brand Imagery</h3>
        <p>Ultra-premium, custom AI-generated brand assets that make your service business look expensive without the $5,000 photoshoot fee.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 4 -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fade-up delay-400">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m22 8-6 4 6 4V8Z"/><rect width="14" height="12" x="2" y="6" rx="2" ry="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Short-Form Content</h3>
        <p>We transform your long-form videos into high-performing, platform-native clips for TikTok and Reels to dominate social feeds.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 5 -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fade-up delay-500">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/><path d="M14.05 2a9 9 0 0 1 8 7.94"/><path d="M14.05 6A5 5 0 0 1 18 10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Automated Follow-ups</h3>
        <p>Never lose a lead again. We build automated SMS and email systems that engage prospects the second they contact you.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 6 -->
      <div class="service-card animate-fade-up delay-600">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Reputation Management</h3>
        <p>Put your 5-star reviews on autopilot. We implement systems to automatically collect positive feedback from happy clients.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .services-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .header-content {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); /* Diubah ke 3 kolom */
    gap: 2rem; /* Sedikit dirapatkan agar muat dengan indah */
    max-width: 1200px; /* Diperlebar untuk memuat 3 kolom */
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .service-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background-color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.03);
    border-radius: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.08);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  /* Top accent border on hover */
  .service-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 4px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    background-color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }
  
  .service-card:hover::before {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .service-card:hover .icon-wrapper {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.7);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 450px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .service-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
